== 概念與美術 ==
佩芮提到《微笑》是關於「在隧道盡頭尋找光明」以及尋回笑容的專輯，而這概念則源自她於2017年的事業低潮以及跟奥兰多·布鲁姆的關係低谷。她亦提到曾經歷抑鬱並抱有自殺的想法，而最後把自己拯救出來的是「感恩之情」<ref>{{Cite news |date=2020-06-29 |title=Katy Perry reveals she felt suicidal during 2017 split from Orlando Bloom |first=Janet |last=Krajcsik |url=https://www.pennlive.com/entertainment/2020/06/katy-perry-reveals-she-felt-suicidal-during-2017-split-from-orlando-bloom.html |access-date=2020-07-09 |newspaper={{tsl|en|The Patriot-News|The Patriot-News|The Patriot-News}} |archive-date=2020-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903231223/https://www.pennlive.com/entertainment/2020/06/katy-perry-reveals-she-felt-suicidal-during-2017-split-from-orlando-bloom.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。佩芮也形容《微笑》為她「邁向光明的旅程，當中包括抗逆、希望與愛的故事」<ref>{{cite tweet |user=katyperry |number=1281228120905793538 |date=2020-07-09 |title=I wrote the title track from the album when I was coming through one of the darkest periods of my life and had lost my smile. This whole album is my journey towards the light – with stories of resilience, hope, and love. ♥️}}</ref>。

在專輯的封面中，佩芮扮成「戴上紅色鼻子與身穿藍白格子衣服的憂愁小丑」，並身處專輯的名稱《Smile》之上。封面透過一個[[推特|推特]]遊戲公開，由她的歌迷與追蹤者分享關於專輯的推文以讓封面釋出<ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9415792/katy-perry-reveal-smile-album-cover |title=Katy Perry Proves She's the Ultimate 'Pop' Star With Playful KP5 Album Cover Reveal |magazine=Billboard |last=Kaufman |first=Gil |date=2020-07-09 |accessdate=2020-07-09 |archive-date=2020-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903231249/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9415792/katy-perry-reveal-smile-album-cover |dead-url=no }}</ref>。佩芮於8月推出專輯的CD與圖膠唱片限量版，當中包括五個不同封面的版本，並開放五天時間限時預購<ref name="Alternate Covers">References for limited edition artwork:
