佩芮於2020年8月20日公開〈What Makes a Woman〉作為宣傳單曲發行<ref>{{cite tweet|user=katyperry|number=1296463767920873474|date=2020-08-20|title= May I present... the next taste of 🙂#SMILE🙂 before it comes out NEXT! FRIDAY! (AUGUST 28TH!) What Makes A Woman is out now http://katy.to/wmaw and go to http://katy.to/preordersmile to pre-order the whole record!!!|accessdate=2020-08-22}}</ref>。她亦在個人的[[Vevo|Vevo]]頻道公開了歌曲的原音樂版現場版<ref>{{cite web|title=Katy Perry - What Makes A Woman (Acoustic Video)|url=https://youtube.com/watch?v=q_JTAO-8xgc|date=2020-08-20|accessdate=2020-08-22|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821212500/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q_JTAO-8xgc|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並曾在同年6月稱歌曲是獻給自己即將出生的女兒<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Rowley|first=Glenn|date=2020-08-20|title=Katy Perry Unveils New Song 'What Makes A Woman' Dedicated to Her Unborn Daughter: Listen|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9408644/katy-perry-what-makes-a-woman|accessdate=2020-08-22|magazine=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821232923/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9408644/katy-perry-what-makes-a-woman|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 商業成績 ==
《微笑》發行首週以約50,000張[[专辑等价单位|专辑等价单位]]（包括約35,000張實際銷量）空降美國[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|《告示牌》二百強專輯榜]]第5位，成為佩芮第五張打進榜單前10位的專輯榜。然而這是她自2008年的《[[花漾派對|花漾派對]]》後首張未能登上榜單冠軍的專輯。專輯的收錄曲亦在2020年9月12日當週獲得總共1,900萬次自選串流媒體<ref name="BB200debut">{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9445521/taylor-swift-ties-whitney-houston-folklore-tops-billboard-200-sixth-week|first=Keith|last=Caulfield|title=Taylor Swift Ties Whitney Houston for Most Weeks at No. 1 Among Women in Billboard 200's History|magazine=Billboard|date=2020-09-06|accessdate=2020-09-06|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906192953/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9445521/taylor-swift-ties-whitney-houston-folklore-tops-billboard-200-sixth-week|dead-url=no}}</ref>。專輯發行首週亦空降[[加拿大专辑榜|加拿大专辑榜]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fyimusicnews.ca/articles/2020/09/07/taylor-swift-continues-her-albums-chart-domination|title=Taylor Swift Continues Her Albums Chart Domination|publisher=FYI Music News|date=2020-09-07|accessdate=2020-09-08|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525190250/https://www.fyimusicnews.ca/articles/2020/09/07/taylor-swift-continues-her-albums-chart-domination|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[英國專輯排行榜|英國專輯排行榜]]第5位，當中在英國首週售出約8,579張專輯等價單位<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Masterson|first=James|date=2020-09-04|title=Charts analysis: Streaming powers Nines to albums summit|url=https://www.musicweek.com/analysis/read/charts-analysis-streaming-powers-nines-to-albums-summit/081018|magazine={{tsl|en|Music Week|音樂週刊|Music Week}}|accessdate=2020-09-05|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525190206/https://www.musicweek.com/analysis/read/charts-analysis-streaming-powers-nines-to-albums-summit/081018|dead-url=no}}</ref>。　

在愛爾蘭，專輯首週空降[[愛爾蘭專輯榜|愛爾蘭專輯榜]]第9位，成為佩芮於當地連續第五張打進前10位的專輯<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2020-09-04|title=Taylor Swift denies Metallica Irish Number 1|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/taylor-swift-denies-metallica-the-number-1-spot-on-the-official-irish-albums-chart__30914/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907101618/https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/taylor-swift-denies-metallica-the-number-1-spot-on-the-official-irish-albums-chart__30914/|archive-date=2020-09-07|access-date=2020-09-07|website=[[愛爾蘭唱片音樂協會|Irish Recorded Music Association]]|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《微笑》於首週空降[[澳大利亚唱片业协会榜|澳大利亚唱片业协会榜]]第2位，僅次於[[金属乐队|金属乐队]]同週發行的現場專輯《{{tsl|en|S&M2|金屬製品與舊金山交響樂團 現場演出實錄|金屬製品與舊金山交響樂團 現場演出實錄}}》<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2020-09-07|title=ARIA Albums Chart|url=https://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/albums-chart|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200823153309/https://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/albums-chart|archive-date=2020-09-07|access-date=2020-09-07|publisher=[[澳大利亚唱片业协会|Australian Recording Industry Association]]}}</ref>。在紐西蘭，專輯首週空降[[新西兰官方音乐榜|新西兰官方音乐榜]]第4位<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=New Zealand Albums Top 40 Chart|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=4931|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907052724/https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=4931|archive-date=2020-09-07|access-date=2020-09-07|publisher=[[新西兰唱片音乐协会|Recorded Music NZ]]}}</ref>，而專輯在日本則空降[[Oricon公信榜|Oricon公信榜]]第39位<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2020-09-07|title=Oricon Albums Chart|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/w/2020-09-07/p/4/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902064019/https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/w/2020-09-07/p/4/|archive-date=2020-09-07|access-date=|publisher=[[Oricon|Oricon]]}}</ref>。在德國，專輯首週空降當地專輯榜第14位<ref name="Germany">{{cite web|url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/album-details-425013|title=Offizielle Deutsche Charts|publisher=[[GfK娛樂榜單|Gfk Entertainment Charts]]|date=2020-09-04|accessdate=2020-09-15|archive-date=